room_title: Escape room "Eddy's Organs" by Escape House in Rexburg
review: We tried out the Eddy's Organs room. I took my daughter and two of her friends, we had a great time. I was grateful that they were all musical as I can't read a note and would never have gotten out lol. Can't wait to try another room.
